
Problem Statement  : Student–Course System
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
A college wants to develop a web application to manage students and the courses they are enrolled in. Each student is enrolled in one course, while a course can have multiple students.

The application should be built using ASP.NET Core MVC with Dapper to handle database operations.

The system should:

Store Course details (CourseId, CourseName)
Store Student details (StudentId, StudentName, CourseId)
Implement a one-to-many relationship between Course and Student using a foreign key

Application should Provide 
Fetch student data along with course details
Fetch course details data along with  students who are enrolled

The goal is to demonstrate how foreign key relationships, navigation properties, and data retrieval using dapper.

